---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SectionHeading from "../components/SectionHeading.astro";
import Achievement from "../components/Achievement.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Chris Berry - Author">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Me</h1>
      <img
        src="/images/author-photo.png"
        alt="Author photo"
        class="float-right ml-8 mb-8 w-64 h-74 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
      />
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl mb-4">
          Hello there! I’m Chris Berry, a multi-talented author with a distinctive
          background and diverse interests. Raised in a small town, I became
          captivated by literature and storytelling at an early age. After
          serving in the military and working as a police officer in the Kansas
          City metro area, I’ve gone on to pursue software development but never
          abandoned my passion for writing.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          I’ve written numerous books acclaimed for their gripping plots,
          dynamic characters, and fast-paced action. As an enthusiastic reader
          myself, I recognize the significance of storytelling and strive to
          create books that keep readers engaged and engrossed.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Apart from writing, I’m also an accomplished photographer and digital
          artist. I strongly believe that creativity is a fundamental aspect of
          human expression and draws inspiration from a variety of sources.
        </p>
        Whether writing, taking photographs, or creating digital art, I am constantly
        exploring new ways to express myself and connect with others through my artistic
        and storytelling abilities.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

