  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-4 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
    <SectionHeading title="Writing Philosophy" />
    <p class="text-gray-300">
      I believe in creating stories that not only entertain but also challenge
      readers to think differently about the world around them. Each book is a
      journey we take together, exploring the depths of human experience through
      the power of words.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section  class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-4 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
    <SectionHeading title="Contact" />
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
      I love hearing from readers! You can reach me through social media or send
      me an email at [your email].
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-300">
      For media inquiries and speaking engagements, please contact my literary
      agent: [Agent Name] at [agent email/contact].
    </p>
